  "body": "Some of the points I discussed with Stefan about the DNS issues some users have been reporting:\n\n- [x] Setup a rocket pool besu node (seems more likely to encounter DNS issues)\n- [x] Evaluate the possibility of hiding the DNS timeout warning when node already has peers.\n- [x] Re-check interval we use to resolve the DNS (we retry every 10 minutes when DNS gets updated every 12 hours) Maybe only re-check if we haven't successfully resolved the DNS yet.\n- [ ] Investigate a more complex improvement which would be not collect all DNS entries at once and try in batches. ",
