    "body": "Closing this issue after some investigation with findings described below:\r\n1- Rocket pool setup has presented no DNS issues when done on aws.\r\n2 - Probably not the best of the improvements since this could hide some possible configuration issues. \r\n3 - Has been attempted before and advised to not move forward with. Also it provides no improvements since after Tuweni DNS resolves the tree it keeps track of the latest seq number resolved and won't retry resolving the tree.\r\n4 - Has also been attempted before and suggested to be done in Tuweni (see #1707 and )",
